OL,7,FA wind turbine which can be set alight
OL,8,Fto help people working in the region's
OL,9,FTeesside's growing wind energy
OL,10,Findustry has been launched on
OL,11,FTeesside.JThe huge training tower in
OL,12,FHartlepool is the first of its kind in
OL,13,Fthe world and can be set on fire
OL,14,Frepeatedly to help green energy
OL,15,Fworkers learn how to tackle
OL,16,Femergencies which will be as close to
OL,17,Freal life as possible.JThe growth of
OL,18,Fthe North East's renewable energy
OL,19,Fsector means there is increased demand
OL,20,Ffor skills in responding to
OL,21,Femergencies.
