OL,7,FCharlie Whellans from Cleveland Fire
OL,8,FBrigade Risk Management says "We have
OL,9,Fthe ability to provide a live fire
OL,10,Ftraining scenario to replicate
OL,11,Frealistic conditions for course
OL,12,Fparticipants giving them the
OL,13,Fopportunity to experience what it
OL,14,Fwould be like in a real life
OL,15,Fincident."JWorkers will also be
OL,16,Ftrained on VR headsets to help
OL,17,Funderstand how to approach different
OL,18,Fscenarios in an emergency situation.
OL,19,FLuke Anderson from MBG Offshore said:
OL,20,F"The renewable industry, particularly
OL,21,Foffshore wind and stuff, has not
OL,22,Freached its peak yet. It's probably
OL,23,Fnot going to reach its peak for the
OL,24,Fnext ten years so stuff like this is a
OL,25,Fnecessity. Especially for the offshore
OL,26,Fengineering world, it's well needed.
